title: Enjoy the Journey
itunes:title: Enjoy the Journey
description:
Many people are living for the mountain top moments, but those moments are few and far between. Life is about the journey, not the destination. Learn to have joy for the journey!Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love. To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
